Package: TensorEEG
Type: Package
Title: Physics-Constrained Tensor EEG Simulation Engine
Version: 0.9.1
Authors@R: person("Yiming", "Shen", email = "yiming.shen001@umb.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Generates synthetic EEG data as 3rd-order tensors using physically constrained mixing matrices (Fibonacci grid, Graph Laplacian) and manifold dynamics (Lie algebra drift) to benchmark BCI algorithms.
